              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/26691400/" class="">第1章 次贷危机改变了世界</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/4430032/" class=" " title="z">z</a>
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
